InterviewDescriptions.MFP 100 Deloris Johnson Nason 9-22-2011: Abstract: Deloris Jenkins discusses her experiences growing up in Gainesville, Florida, including her time at Lincoln High School. She reflects on Lincoln, her mentors there, and her involvement in activities at the school. Mrs. Jenkins recalls highly dedicated instructors and administrators, and describes a similar overall ethic in the wider community. In discussing more recent years, she also shares her thoughts about her career working in the Physical Plant at the University of Florida.
